s=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我咁大個第一次 有d驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7ad926a67f7bb1bb4038aef4f644bb41127dcde","tid":245082,"uid":11030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T03:45:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>痛唔痛？ 個身有無？出過水痘未？ 係唔係集中係一邊身？</blockquote><br />\n唔痛 得前臂有<br />\n未出過<br />\n唔係 兩隻手都有"},{"pid":"291cb6ad323260e57cfb96cbff98986a0345f67c","tid":245082,"uid":93753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T03:46:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>敏感<br />\n<br />\n我試過，成身都有，痕到仆街<br />\n你諗下你有無食咩，或者掂到咩污糟野</blockquote><br />\n同埋你去睇醫生啦，早d 睇受少d 苦</blockquote><br />\n好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我以為幾日就好番<br />\n點知越出越多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n剃完毛之後個日就生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能真是敏感</blockquote><br />\n我果時係去Bali旅行,係個沙灘到玩，玩完就咁。拖左兩三日先睇醫生，後悔死我。因為佢係要成個幾禮拜先會退。我係痕到想死，覺都訓唔到先去睇。所以你趁你依家岩岩起就快快去睇啦！！<br />\n<br />\n果陣我搽類固醇藥膏再加食敏感藥，好快就退"},{"pid":"eb352480ce3693f8e7a39d1f26ba52cf7aa01aa1","tid":245082,"uid":30431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T03:46:56.000Z","msg":"我都係咁 唔知對咩敏感 開頭得手臂有<br />\n聽日手掌底勁多 我睇左醫生比左隻lotion幾好用<br />\n平曬加淡色"},{"pid":"3292c9d867bc8696bfb20d5866ffb02f8f3149ab","tid":245082,"uid":15379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T03:47:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我前幾日又係生咗好多粒粒係手臂 腳指罅 同埋腳板底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n平時唔會痕 但一搔就會痕</blockquote><br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我咁大個第一次 有d驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n通常春夏季會出，手或腳會有水泡，手掌手背都有機會生，真菌感染"},{"pid":"3fb15c91d09cec13c90632a4be196954dbe988d4","tid":245082,"uid":93752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T03:47:14.000Z","msg":"睇醫生啦，仲諗。 <br />\n普通家庭醫生都得，再唔係就皮膚科醫生。"},{"pid":"3559c2ba30f576476860cf01b156e2eac2a7fab5","tid":245082,"uid":11030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T03:48:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果頂唔順就用含有類固醇既野茶<br />\n<br />\n利申同你有同一樣既野 尾已斷</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我老豆又比左支Fluocinonide cream<br />\n唔知乜柒嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n市面上有乜膏有類固醇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbbe19d8dea6b0f94572548219a4df038c6336b7","tid":245082,"uid":29166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T03:48:28.000Z","msg":"rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9461b0f12d3ebd13c355c9afd2edb0f1475e3e11","tid":245082,"uid":53591,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T03:49:11.000Z","msg":"應該係 尖銳 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n自己google 搵下"},{"pid":"5023d23abc25a3be19c4ea96cf9e294c91c4bb4a","tid":245082,"uid":11030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T03:49:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>應該係 尖銳 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n自己google 搵下</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又恰我"},{"pid":"758e228dd52e847c5dd4901e883828483f0aab4d","tid":245082,"uid":1836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T03:51:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我前幾日又係生咗好多粒粒係手臂 腳指罅 同埋腳板底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n平時唔會痕 但一搔就會痕</blockquote><br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我咁大個第一次 有d驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n試下換咗啲床單同被單 有可能生瘙"},{"pid":"1313b51aeb0eb84a170346b00e5a067a03771cde","tid":245082,"uid":93807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T03:51:59.000Z","msg":"我呢幾日全家都有呢啲粒粒，係有野咬"},{"pid":"f92ca355916bd95d478d865f11f1eebb54844cfb","tid":245082,"uid":90497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T03:52:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>痛唔痛？ 個身有無？出過水痘未？ 係唔係集中係一邊身？</blockquote><br />\n唔痛 得前臂有<br />\n未出過<br />\n唔係 兩隻手都有</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n黎二三日作息定時， 唔好打丁，沖涼沖乾淨，唔好食熱氣野。 應該會無事。  <br />\n再有先睇醫生。"},{"pid":"4a5ef345092e0d9ee2c2148e775c4ecb0a535f7e","tid":245082,"uid":11030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T03:53:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/16/115228_a1c1258381242754b2aa057af700c00a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F16%2F115228_a1c1258381242754b2aa057af700c00a.jpg&h=ce113469&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n清晰版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中間白周圍紅<br />\n擠唔到野的"},{"pid":"a209193356ffb671a19626f5cc84958a3c0d4d9d","tid":245082,"uid":11030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T03:54:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>痛唔痛？ 個身有無？出過水痘未？ 係唔係集中係一邊身？</blockquote><br />\n唔痛 得前臂有<br />\n未出過<br />\n唔係 兩隻手都有</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n黎二三日作息定時， 唔好打丁，沖涼沖乾淨，唔好食熱氣野。 應該會無事。  <br />\n再有先睇醫生。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無打過丁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n作息都正常<br />\n最近好似食左好多蝦片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfadeae445bda709b0e1a5aad9307cfab4852a54","tid":245082,"uid":30431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T03:54:32.000Z","msg":"樓主試下e技<br />\n嚴重都1夜ko<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/16/115415_a00fd57e8877946ad63f082234c786c0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F16%2F115415_a00fd57e8877946ad63f082234c786c0.jpg&h=f3cbcbaf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"728e6bd1bedd10fc0380fb7869b53baca42957bc","tid":245082,"uid":21059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T03:54:50.000Z","msg":"你係咪用剃刀剃？<br />\n有時剃刀既刀片污糟，剃完之後皮膚薄左係會好易痕，r多幾下入左細菌個啲就會敏感<br />\n我之前都有咁既情況 最後去睇醫生攞藥膏擦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cee8bf9243bea0a1d5203562f184a2a9267dfcb9","tid":245082,"uid":14269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T03:55:11.000Z","msg":"應該係皮膚發炎姐<br />\n我有濕疹，個樣的確係幾似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但濕疹會紅到一達達咁<br />\n你睇落又好似冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32a640baa806c1883831775a1ed364fa3631f1f3","tid":245082,"uid":11030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T03:55:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>敏感<br />\n<br />\n我試過，成身都有，痕到仆街<br />\n你諗下你有無食咩，或者掂到咩污糟野</blockquote><br />\n同埋你去睇醫生啦，早d 睇受少d 苦</blockquote><br />\n好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我以為幾日就好番<br />\n點知越出越多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n剃完毛之後個日就生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能真是敏感</blockquote><br />\n我果時係去Bali旅行,係個沙灘到玩，玩完就咁。拖左兩三日先睇醫生，後悔死我。因為佢係要成個幾禮拜先會退。我係痕到想死，覺都訓唔到先去睇。所以你趁你依家岩岩起就快快去睇啦！！<br />\n<br />\n果陣我搽類固醇藥膏再加食敏感藥，好快就退</blockquote><br />\n好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有乜市面藥膏推介下"},{"pid":"13481a35b1dda3a246fefa6db5b630d0cde7f720","tid":245082,"uid":11030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T03:57:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你係咪用剃刀剃？<br />\n有時剃刀既刀片污糟，剃完之後皮膚薄左係會好易痕，r多幾下入左細菌個啲就會敏感<br />\n我之前都有咁既情況 最後去睇醫生攞藥膏擦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n買膏搽先<br />\n聽日唔得再睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"652e5be6922c3473038c9d706ff0cf5cff53a7df","tid":245082,"uid":11030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T03:58:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主試下e技<br />\n嚴重都1夜ko<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/16/115415_a00fd57e8877946ad63f082234c786c0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F16%2F115415_a00fd57e8877946ad63f082234c786c0.jpg&h=f3cbcbaf&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji